Class BaseTree

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.data.spx.BaseTree
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Tree
public class BaseTree
extends Object
implements Tree

A default implementation of the Tree interface.

Although none of the methods here are marked as synchronized, all inserts and searches are synchronized internally using the read-write lock mechanism provided by com.esri.mo2.util.RWLock. Therefore external synchronization is not needed.

See Also:
RWLock, Serialized Form
